true?

MR. KELLY: Objection. Same objection. Goes beyond the scope as to what
was -- what was prior to his direct testimony. Your Honor, it's also
hearsay too.

THE COURT: It's a party. (Referring to counsel table.).

Overruled.

THE WITNESS: Yes. He volunteered to give a sampling, yes.

Q. (BY MR. BAKER) He had, you had told Mr. Simpson that you had some
problems because you had blood at his house. And he said give me a
