Simpson's finger, didn't he?

MR. KELLY: Objection. Beyond the scope, Your Honor.

THE COURT: Overruled.

THE WITNESS: He cleaned his finger, yes and put a Band-Aid on it.

Q. And you looked at Mr. Simpson's fingers at that time and his hands
at that time, didn't you?

A. I looked at his hand, yes.

Q. And he had one cut that was on the knuckle of -- or the middle
