MR. LAMBERT: I must be wrong. It's the summary of voluminous records.
Exception is --

MR. PETROCELLI: If it's in sequence.

MR. LAMBERT: Maybe it's 14 --

MR. PETROCELLI: It might be in the 14 hundred sequence, Judge.

