Q. Let me show you what's been previously marked as exhibit 202.

Do you recognize this document, Mr. Fung?

(The instrument herein referred to as crime scene checklist was marked
for identification as Plaintiffs' Exhibit No. 202.)

A. Yes, I do.

Q. What is that document?

A. That is a crime scene checklist?

Q. And tell us how that document gets generated?

A. Well, when a call gets made to a criminalist, they start filling it
