MR. LAMBERT: Objection. No foundation.

MR. BLASIER: Do you know?

THE COURT: Overruled.

You may answer.

THE WITNESS: I am not aware of any further testing done on item No. 1.

Q. (BY MR. BLASIER) Now, is it an acceptable procedure in your mind to
