The aorta shows two little blood vessels down below the cut with a are
the origins of two arteries that come out of the aorta, because the
aorta gives rise to the entire blood system, the entire arterial
system in the body, and the blood vessels come out of the aorta and
they look just like that.

And what is significant is that the soft tissues, the fat and other
soft tissues behind the aorta, is totally infiltrated with blood.

