A. Most of the hairs were long perhaps up to a foot in length. There
was about 35 of them all forcibly removed. There were a number of
short cut hairs that were darker Caucasian those were the two
Caucasian types of hair that were found.

Q. Did you have occasion to compare those hairs with any known hairs?

A. I did, yes.

Q. And what known hairs did you compare them with?

A. Okay. I compared all the head hairs Caucasian hairs with the two
white individuals Nicole Brown Simpson, Ron Goldman a Negroid head
hair was compared that with O.J. Simpson initially.

Q. And what kind of examination -- strike that.

Did you perform the same or different examinations in terms of your
